    "title": "Eye certain. Finger Lightning. Aim Death.",
    "description": "Seraph effect: +420% critical hit damage (scales), plus the usual Jakobs sniper crit bonus.\n\nBonuses: higher zoom, fire rate, reload speed, and magazine size.\nPenalties: reduced base damage and slightly lower accuracy."
  },
  "notes": "Slightly higher headshot damage than a comparable Muckamuck, with a faster fire rate.\nWith heavy critical stacking (for example Critical Ascensi0n), Muckamuck can overtake it.\n+100% crit adds about +14.7% crit damage here, versus about +38% on typical Jakobs snipers and +50% on most non-Jakobs snipers.\nZoom was once incorrect; later fixed to a higher-than-normal value.\nWith a Hyperion scope it reaches 11.6x zoom, the highest of any sniper rifle.",
